  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/2eef298d2df62844facce7d031d60a53.poster.avif?t=1598029312\" width=376 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/2eef298d2df62844facce7d031d60a53.webm?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/2eef298d2df62844facce7d031d60a53.mp4?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pre-Shave is a narrative shaving simulator game. <br><br>You play as Saam preparing to get ready for a trip. Explore the anxieties of his nervous mind, thwart your excessive body hair with the use of your powerful shaving gear, and don't forget to brush your teeth!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/87024e8022407586b68c785ecbd3c47f.poster.avif?t=1598029312\" width=380 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/87024e8022407586b68c785ecbd3c47f.webm?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/87024e8022407586b68c785ecbd3c47f.mp4?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Wacky physics</strong> with unique controls<br></li><li> <strong>\"Realistic\"</strong> shaving mechanics<br></li><li> <strong>Multiple gadgets </strong>to groom and clean with<br></li><li><strong>Lots of body and facial hair</strong> for you to sculpt / personalize<br></li><li> <strong>Achievements</strong> to unlock your true hairy potential</li></ul><br>NOTE: This is a very short game. If you get stuck try holding the phone up to your face.<br><br>Originally created for #WineJam 2019",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/2eef298d2df62844facce7d031d60a53.poster.avif?t=1598029312\" width=376 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/2eef298d2df62844facce7d031d60a53.webm?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/2eef298d2df62844facce7d031d60a53.mp4?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pre-Shave is a narrative shaving simulator game. <br><br>You play as Saam preparing to get ready for a trip. Explore the anxieties of his nervous mind, thwart your excessive body hair with the use of your powerful shaving gear, and don't forget to brush your teeth!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/87024e8022407586b68c785ecbd3c47f.poster.avif?t=1598029312\" width=380 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/87024e8022407586b68c785ecbd3c47f.webm?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383270/extras/87024e8022407586b68c785ecbd3c47f.mp4?t=1598029312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Wacky physics</strong> with unique controls<br></li><li> <strong>\"Realistic\"</strong> shaving mechanics<br></li><li> <strong>Multiple gadgets </strong>to groom and clean with<br></li><li><strong>Lots of body and facial hair</strong> for you to sculpt / personalize<br></li><li> <strong>Achievements</strong> to unlock your true hairy potential</li></ul><br>NOTE: This is a very short game. If you get stuck try holding the phone up to your face.<br><br>Originally created for #WineJam 2019",
